                <h3>Transportation</h3>
                <p>
                    If you're looking for a convenient and time-saving way to get around town, private cars offer an
                    excellent solution. Whether you choose to hail a taxi or book a ride through popular ride-sharing
                    services like Uber and Careem, you'll be able to quickly and easily reach your destination with just
                    a few clicks.
                    While Alexandria is a city that's ideally suited for walking, particularly in its central and
                    downtown districts, there are times when longer journeys around the city are necessary. Fortunately,
                    there are several easy and cost-effective transportation options available to visitors.
                </p>
                <p>

                    Whether you're looking to explore the city's many attractions or simply need to get from point A to
                    point B, private cars can provide a comfortable and reliable means of transportation. For longer
                    journeys around the city, visitors have the following easy and cost effective options:
                </p>
